@startuml
title Feature 015 sequence: partner reports, commissions and documents

actor "Партнер" as Partner
actor "Бухгалтер" as Accountant
actor "Финансовый контролер" as Controller
participant "Frontend React\n/report/order-history\n/report/info-reciept" as Frontend
participant "partner-reporting API" as Reporting
participant "order module" as Order
participant "bonus-wallet module" as Wallet
participant "compensation plan" as Compensation
participant "payment module" as Payment
database "partner-reporting DB" as DB
collections "S3/MinIO documents" as Storage

Partner -> Frontend: Открывает /report/order-history
Frontend -> Reporting: GET /reports/summary?period&catalog&bonusProgram
Reporting -> DB: Найти report_period
Reporting -> Order: Получить агрегаты заказов структуры
Reporting -> Wallet: Получить удержания и reversal events
Reporting -> Compensation: Получить commission rules и accruals
Reporting -> DB: Обновить summary snapshot при необходимости
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportSummaryResponse + STR_MNEMO_* + correlationId
Frontend --> Partner: Сводка продаж, комиссий, удержаний, выплат и сверки

Partner -> Frontend: Фильтрует строки заказов
Frontend -> Reporting: GET /reports/orders?filters&page&size
Reporting -> DB: Найти partner_report_order_line page
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportOrderPageResponse
Partner -> Frontend: Открывает детализацию комиссии
Frontend -> Reporting: GET /reports/orders/{orderNumber}/commission
Reporting -> DB: Получить order line, adjustments, payout reference
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerCommissionDetailResponse

Partner -> Frontend: Открывает /report/info-reciept
Frontend -> Reporting: GET /documents?filters
Reporting -> DB: Найти документы партнера
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportDocumentPageResponse
Partner -> Frontend: Скачивает опубликованный документ
Frontend -> Reporting: POST /documents/{documentId}/download
Reporting -> DB: Проверить ownership, PUBLISHED, version, checksum
Reporting -> Storage: Создать signed download URL
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportDocumentDownloadResponse
Frontend --> Partner: Download URL или localized STR_MNEMO_*

Partner -> Frontend: Запускает XLSX/PDF экспорт
Frontend -> Reporting: POST /exports
Reporting -> DB: Создать partner_report_export
Reporting -> Storage: Сохранить файл экспорта
Reporting -> DB: Пометить READY, row_count, storage_key
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportExportResponse STR_MNEMO_PARTNER_REPORT_EXPORT_READY

Accountant -> Frontend: Публикует готовый документ
Frontend -> Reporting: POST /finance/documents/{documentId}/publish(reasonCode)
Reporting -> DB: Проверить роль, READY, reasonCode
Reporting -> Storage: Проверить checksum файла
Reporting -> DB: Установить PUBLISHED, version, checksum, audit
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportDocumentResponse

Controller -> Frontend: Разбирает расхождение сверки
Frontend -> Reporting: GET /finance/reconciliations?partnerId&period&reason
Reporting -> DB: Получить totals, mismatch reasons, documents, payouts
Reporting -> Payment: Проверить payout status
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportFinanceReconciliationResponse
Controller -> Frontend: Отзывает ошибочный документ
Frontend -> Reporting: POST /finance/documents/{documentId}/revoke(reasonCode)
Reporting -> DB: Установить REVOKED и audit trail
Reporting --> Frontend: PartnerReportDocumentResponse STR_MNEMO_PARTNER_REPORT_RECONCILIATION_MISMATCH
@enduml
